tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE historical_trades (
 trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 trade_date DATE,
 trade_time TIME,
 trade_symbol VARCHAR(50),
 trade_volume INT,
 trade_price DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE historical_trades (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_date DATE,
    stock_symbol VARCHAR(10),
    trade_type VARCHAR(10),
    trade_volume INT
);

CREATE TABLE trade_patterns (
    pattern_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    pattern_name VARCHAR(50),
    description TEXT,
    trade_strategy VARCHAR(100),
    trade_frequency VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE trades (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    stock_symbol VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    trade_date DATE NOT NULL,
    trade_type VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
    trade_price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
    trade_volume INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE trades ( 
   trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
   stock_symbol VARCHAR(50), 
   trade_type VARCHAR(50), 
   trade_volume INT, 
   trade_price DECIMAL(10,2), 
   trade_date DATE 
);

CREATE TABLE stock_prices ( 
   stock_symbol VARCHAR(50) PRIMARY KEY, 
   last_price DECIMAL(10,2), 
   high_price DECIMAL(10,2), 
   low_price DECIMAL(10,2), 
   market_cap DECIMAL(20,2) 
);

CREATE TABLE trade_analysis ( 
   analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
   trade_id INT, 
   analysis_date DATE, 
   trend VARCHAR(50), 
   conclusion VARCHAR(100) 
);

CREATE TABLE trades (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_date DATE,
    symbol VARCHAR(50),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    volume INT
);

CREATE TABLE trade_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_id INT,
    analysis_date DATE,
    trend VARCHAR(50),
    result TEXT
);
